WITHDRAWALDESCRIPTION: Registrant is no longer performing transfer agent functions.

Originally, our plan was to file under Regulation A and to establish our own Transfer Agency services accordingly. However due to evolving market conditions and alterations in our business strategy, we have decided to not pursue a Regulation A offering.

All of Registrant's transfer agency assets and operations were transferred to its parent company DST Systems, Inc (now named SS&C GIDS, Inc.) effective as of January 1, 2023, after which Registrant has not performed transfer agency functions.
Technology and Operations not complete to begin business
Currently not providing and have no plans to provide Transfer Agent services in the future.
